<h1 id="about-illuminous">About Illuminous</h1>
<p>The name Illuminous fits this slot perfectly being filled with bright effects, disco sound and a glass like background that reflects all the lights. The symbols in this slot are gems. There are light effects illustrating any wins, enhancing the gameplay. The slot is also using a great feature Quickspin is calling “Hot Reels” which is sure to get you stoked every time it pops up. There are very few slot’s competing with the sheer number of wilds that Illuminous has.<br>
Follow the light.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game Features</h2>
<p>Using the classic five reel three row setup Illuminous is played using Wilds, the Hot Reel Re-Spin and Hot Reel Free Spins features.</p>
<h3 id="wild">Wild</h3>
<p>Replacing any any and all symbols excepting the free spin symbols we have the Wild. The Hot Reel feature is not altering this symbols effect even if it comes up on a Hot Reel. Also worth mentioning is that wilds wont give multipliers, neither during regular play nor in free spin mode.</p>
<h3 id="hot-reel-respin">Hot Reel Respin</h3>
<p>Hitting two bonus Wild symbols activates one Hot Reel Re-Spin. Meaning two reels burst into flames insuring that at least half of the symbols are Wilds. Getting at least one bonus Wild during a Hot Reel Re-Spin triggers on additional re-spin. In conclusion seeing lots of wilds show up on the screen is how you know big winnings are knocking on you door.</p>
<h3 id="hot-reel-free-spins">Hot Reel Free Spins</h3>
<p>Three bonus Wild symbols on the board is what activating the Hot Reel Free Spin feature. Once this happens the game immediately actives five free spins. During these the three reels containing the activating symbols all becomes Hot Reels and they’re staying that way until all the free spins has been played through. While in free spin mode you can win additional free spins by hitting even more bonus Wild symbols. So with a little luck you could be getting as many as five re-spins with all the accompanying wilds that entails. Few slots are giving odds this good for getting five symbol combinations.</p>
